268
00:14:14,921 --> 00:14:17,858
How are we gonna catch her?

269
00:14:17,924 --> 00:14:19,860
‐ Oh, I already thought of that.

270
00:14:19,926 --> 00:14:22,629
At top speed,
she's as fast as a car, right?

271
00:14:22,696 --> 00:14:24,064
‐ So?

272
00:14:24,130 --> 00:14:26,733
‐ So it should be obvious
how we'll catch her.

273
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:28,935
‐ [yelling]

274
00:14:30,571 --> 00:14:31,672
[engine roaring]

275
00:14:31,738 --> 00:14:34,107
Here they come.

276
00:14:36,677 --> 00:14:38,945
‐ Put the pedal to the metal!

277
00:14:39,012 --> 00:14:40,981
