280
00:14:45,018 --> 00:14:47,053
‐ I don't care! Go faster!

281
00:14:48,622 --> 00:14:51,291
Hi‐yo, Silver!

282
00:14:51,357 --> 00:14:52,659
‐ [gasps]

283
00:14:52,726 --> 00:14:54,060
Uh‐oh!

284
00:14:59,499 --> 00:15:01,702
All right! Bring it!

285
00:15:01,768 --> 00:15:02,969
‐ [laughs]

286
00:15:03,036 --> 00:15:04,671
Now it's on!

287
00:15:07,974 --> 00:15:10,443
Go! There's a duel comin' on!

288
00:15:10,511 --> 00:15:11,612
Giddy‐up, horsey!

289
00:15:11,678 --> 00:15:13,647
Hyah! Hyah!

290
00:15:13,714 --> 00:15:16,049
‐ [yelling]

291
00:15:16,116 --> 00:15:19,319
‐ Now this is the fight
I've been dying to have.

292
00:15:23,890 --> 00:15:25,091
Come on!

293
00:15:25,158 --> 00:15:27,227
Fight me,
you little chickenshit!

294
00:15:30,496 --> 00:15:31,765
[groans]

295
00:15:31,832 --> 00:15:33,433
‐ [gasps]
‐ Hmm?

296
00:15:33,499 --> 00:15:34,601
[tires squeal]

297
00:15:37,704 --> 00:15:40,607
‐ [screams]
‐ [grunts]

298
00:15:43,577 --> 00:15:45,411
‐ Yes! It worked!

299
00:15:47,147 --> 00:15:48,749
‐ [engine roaring]
‐ What the‐‐

300
00:15:48,815 --> 00:15:51,284
It was shallow.

301
00:16:01,528 --> 00:16:04,330
‐ Up to now, I killed
with my fists, my guns,

302
00:16:04,397 --> 00:16:06,933
some grenades, and a sword,
pretty much everything,

303
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,936
everything except a car,
that is.

304
00:16:10,003 --> 00:16:13,507
What you gonna do now,
huh, LLENN?!

305
00:16:14,675 --> 00:16:15,609
‐ [grunts]

306
00:16:18,111 --> 00:16:21,081
[both gasp]

307
00:16:21,948 --> 00:16:24,985
‐ [giggles]

308
00:16:27,854 --> 00:16:28,989
I missed.

309
00:16:30,691 --> 00:16:33,560
‐ Now let's see
how you dodge my bullets.

310
00:16:36,863 --> 00:16:37,998
‐ [yelps]

311
