‐ Did you get her?

312
00:16:42,903 --> 00:16:45,005
‐ A marker hasn't popped up yet.

313
00:16:46,640 --> 00:16:48,308
Oh, there she is!

314
00:16:48,374 --> 00:16:50,911
How the hell
is she still alive?

315
00:16:50,977 --> 00:16:52,913
[sighs] I guess
I just winged her.

316
00:16:52,979 --> 00:16:57,584
I swear, it's either 'cause
she's lucky or small or both.

317
00:16:57,651 --> 00:16:59,886
She's tough to kill.

318
00:16:59,953 --> 00:17:01,655
LLENN: Dang it.

319
00:17:01,722 --> 00:17:05,258
Looks like the end for me.

320
00:17:05,325 --> 00:17:07,828
‐ Do you want me
to get a little closer?

321
00:17:07,894 --> 00:17:09,630
Pito: No. I'm fine where we are.

322
00:17:09,696 --> 00:17:12,432
Are you worried I'll miss her
from here or something?

323
00:17:12,498 --> 00:17:15,569
‐ No. It's just that HP
decreases under water.

324
00:17:15,636 --> 00:17:17,671
She'll die whether
you shoot her or not.

325
00:17:17,738 --> 00:17:20,140
I guess I figured
you'd wanna get closer

326
00:17:20,206 --> 00:17:22,475
so you could look her
in the eyes as she died.

327
00:17:22,543 --> 00:17:26,647
‐ Whoa. About time you got
into the spirit of this.

328
00:17:26,713 --> 00:17:30,584
I'm good here. I don't wanna
take any chances around her.

329
00:17:30,651 --> 00:17:33,920
I'm scared she might kill me
if I drop my guard.

330
00:17:33,987 --> 00:17:36,723
‐ Wait. You're scared? Really?

331
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:40,293
‐ Of course. What do you
think I am, an idiot?

332
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:44,197
Sure, I'm scared,
scared of dying.

333
00:17:44,264 --> 00:17:46,767
That's what makes this
so much fun.

334
00:17:47,968 --> 00:17:50,236
‐ <i>What's Pito waiting for?</i>

335
00:17:50,303 --> 00:17:52,472
<i>Why doesn't she finish me?</i>

336
00:17:52,539 --> 00:17:56,409
<i>Oh, well.</i>
<i>Either way, it's over.</i>

337
00:17:56,476 --> 00:17:59,345
P‐chan: Get up, LLENN!
Don't quit now!

338
00:17:59,412 --> 00:18:01,047
‐ <i>Oh, leave me alone.</i>

339
00:18:01,114 --> 00:18:03,617
‐ Come on! You're not dead yet!

340
00:18:03,684 --> 00:18:08,421
<i>‐ It's not at zero,</i>
<i>but it's getting close.</i>

341
00:18:09,823 --> 00:18:12,358
Fuka: <i>Hang on, LLENN!</i>
<i>I'm almost there!</i>

342
00:18:12,425 --> 00:18:14,795
LLENN: <i>Don't bother.</i>

343
00:18:14,861 --> 00:18:16,229
[gasps]

344
00:18:16,296 --> 00:18:19,232
Fuka: <i>Get ready!</i>
<i>I'm comin' in hot!</i>

345
00:18:19,299 --> 00:18:22,402
‐ Eh, I guess I'll put her
out of her misery now.

346
00:18:22,468 --> 00:18:24,237
Don't want her
to drown to death.

347
00:18:24,304 --> 00:18:27,340
M: I'll pull up
a little closer, then.

348
00:18:27,407 --> 00:18:29,275
["Independence"
by Elza Kanzaki playing]

349
00:18:34,214 --> 00:18:35,982
