What's she doing that for?

350
00:18:36,049 --> 00:18:37,450
M: I don't know.

351
00:18:37,518 --> 00:18:41,121
‐ Maybe it's some kind
of shrimpy pre‐death ritual.

352
00:18:41,187 --> 00:18:42,523
[chuckles]

353
00:18:46,993 --> 00:18:48,494
Now what?!

354
00:18:55,502 --> 00:18:57,137
‐ Hang on!

355
00:18:58,004 --> 00:19:00,507
Pito: Charge!

356
00:19:03,343 --> 00:19:05,378
Don't just sit here!
Go after it!

357
00:19:05,445 --> 00:19:07,080
‐ ♪ Don't discard... ♪
[singing in Japanese]

