361
00:19:12,786 --> 00:19:14,054
‐ Okay.

362
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:15,756
<i>‐ ♪ Meant to be... ♪</i>

363
00:19:15,822 --> 00:19:18,692
‐ Mm, someone's gonna
